{"tid":404437,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［龍門］何君堯'殺無赦'論　袁國強：不可憑一兩字說是否犯法　要看字句背景","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T06:07:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d88842db88b7aa5d63d4703ba6d13f63ace90cbe","tid":404437,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯昨日在添馬公園發起集會，其間站台的屏山鄉事委員會主席曾樹和高叫，提倡港獨者應「殺」，何君堯即和應說「無赦」，更指「（搞港獨）啲人唔殺咗佢做咩」，引起關注。律政司長袁國強今中午見記者時表示，不評論個別事件，但指是否構成違反刑事法「要整體去睇」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n袁國強解釋說，「語言的話，要睇講字句及背景，不可單憑一兩個字，亦要睇當時用這個字或說話嘅意思係點」，強調法庭會參考整個背景再作結論。至於是否有需要作進一步行動，他說「用返法庭用嘅原則」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，若然有任何人認為需要跟進事件，可以依照一貫程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n袁國強另強調，「港獨」不符香港憲制及法律地位，看不到這時候鼓吹「港獨」對香港有任何好處。他續說，香港現時面對很多問題，認為聚焦討論其他問題更有建設性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505710862542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505710862542&d=dBg6tSW81F0Leg6ahdWzMXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=03876670\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505710862542&h=9618060d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505710862542</a>"},{"pid":"320a1ed49fbbeadf8d5e9842451b6d8081bcfd9c","tid":404437,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"屌錯台sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}